cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on action recognition using spatio-temporal modeling in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel convolutional network architecture that balances performance and model complexity, which is relevant to machine learning (cs.LG). The use of convolutional networks and deep learning also suggests the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
